#. <section class="sutta" id="sn32.57"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn32.57:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 32"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 32"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.57:0.2"
msgid "1. Valāhakavagga"
msgstr "1. Gods of the Clouds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn32.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Vassavalāhakasutta"
msgstr "57. Gods of the Rainy Clouds"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn32.57:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated at one side that mendicant said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yenekadā devo vassatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why sometimes it rains?”"

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.4"
msgid "“Santi, bhikkhu, vassavalāhakā nāma devā."
msgstr "“Mendicant, there are what are called gods of the rainy clouds."

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.5"
msgid "Tesaṃ yadā evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "Sometimes they think:"

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.6"
msgid ""
"‘yannūna mayaṃ sakāya ratiyā vaseyyāmā’ti, tesaṃ taṃ cetopaṇidhimanvāya devo "
"vassati."
msgstr ""
"‘Why don’t we revel in our own kind of enjoyment?’ Then, in accordance with "
"their wish, it becomes rainy."

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yenekadā devo vassatī”ti."
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why sometimes it rains.”"

msgctxt "sn32.57:1.8"
msgid "Sattapaññāsamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn32.57:1.9"
msgid "Sattapaññāsasuttantaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn32.57:1.10"
msgid "Valāhakavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn32.57:2.1"
msgid "Suddhikaṃ sucaritañca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn32.57:2.2"
msgid "dānūpakārapaññāsaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn32.57:2.3"
msgid "Sītaṃ uṇhañca abbhañca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn32.57:2.4"
msgid "vātavassavalāhakāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn32.57:2.5"
msgid "Valāhakasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on gods of the clouds are complete."
